snippet.title: Nikon D850: Award-winning Sports Photographer Delly Carr
snippet.description:
When preparing to launch the D850, we challenged Nikon Ambassador Delly Carr to capture the image of his lifetime. 

Right before the shoot, Delly suffered an ischemic stroke. He was unable pick up his camera. After three months of recovery he was able to return to the set for the toughest challenge yet, to prove himself yet again and capture the image of his lifetime.

This is Delly‚Äôs story.

snippet.title: SKINCARE BATTLE ü•ä - The Best Barrier Serum Krave Beauty VS Stratia #Shorts
snippet.description:
Skincare this or that putting the Krave Beauty Great Barrier Relief Serum up against the Stratia Liquid Gold. Which is the best barrier supporting moisturiser

Hey guys and welcome back to Mad About Skin.. In todays video I want to compete and contrast the stratia liquid gold and the Krave Great Barrier Relief Serum to work out which is the best barrier supporting serum for your skincare routine.

The Krave Great Barrier Relief Serum claims to be able to hydrate the skin whilst also soothing it, repairing the skin barrier and calming inflammation.

The Stratia Liquid Gold promises to hydrate the skin, boost barrier function in the skin through the use of ceramides and calm and soothe irritation.

Both cant be the best so which would I pick for my skin care routine - keep watching to find out.

I would love to know what your own thoughts are on these products and which you would choose for you own skincare routine so let me know in the comments below.

In Jiangnan of the Republic of China, a young woman named Zi Tao (Hu Jing) came to the Su family, a wealthy country. Since Zi Tao stepped into Su's house, the comfortable living conditions of Mr. Su, his wife, concubines, and children, headed by the eldest wife (played by Dai Chunrong), have completely changed.
